{"id": "1417986017557741599", "channel_id": "1402538040253087766", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "uhh, <@272394963642220545> is our resident specialist and can walk you through the process easier, but in short it's basically\n\n- create a github account\n- fork the official BIAV repository (https://github.com/BIAVGit/Morimens-Localizations/tree/main) so you have your own copy of it to work on\n- make a csv file with all of the lines that you changed, which you do in your own fork\n- submit a pull request to the main BIAV repository afterwards, which creates a submission that Ace/team can review and approve to confirm the changes", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T21:30:11.492000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["272394963642220545"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 4}
